    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chicken stock</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up, then cook for 3-4 min or until slightly reduced</p><p>Once reduced, add the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and the <strong>chopped dill & chives </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy lemon & herb sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
