    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Trim the woody ends off your <strong>asparagus</strong></p><p>Tip: Alternatively, bend the woody ends of the asparagus until they snap!</p><p>Add the <strong>trimmed green beans</strong> and <strong>asparagus</strong> to the reserved pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) then bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>",
