      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>bacon wrapped basa </strong>with the<strong> roasted potatoes </strong>and the <strong>cooked green beans & asparagus </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>creamy lemon & herb sauce </strong>over everything</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
